name: Nike Pro Dri-FIT
Description: Much more than a base layer, the Nike Pro Dri-FIT Shorts hug you with lightweight fabric that keeps you feeling dry, cool and supported from warm-ups through to cool-downs. They're made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres in a stretchy design that helps you move at full intensity during your toughest workouts or competitions.

name: Nike ESC
Description: The iconic WW2 deck jacket serves as inspiration for this lightweight and comfortable layering staple. Its waist-length design features a covered button placket, darted patterning for shape and a convertible collar for easy wear. An internal carrying strap lets you sling it over your shoulder when you're not wearing it for hands-free convenience.

name: Liverpool F.C. 2022/23 Match Home
Category: Men's Nike Dri-FIT ADV Football Shirt
Description: Like other shirts from our Match collection, this one pairs authentic design details with lightweight, quick-drying fabric to help keep the world's biggest football stars cool and comfortable on the pitch. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Liverpool F.C. 2022/23 Stadium Home
Description: Like other shirts from our Stadium collection, this one pairs replica design details with sweat-wicking fabric to give you a game-ready look inspired by your favourite team. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: NikeCourt Dri-FIT
Description: Made from soft knit fabric that's made from 100% recycled polyester fibres, the NikeCourt Dri-FIT Polo is a classic-looking, sweat-wicking court staple.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Miler
Description: Take on your daily route with the Nike Dri-FIT Miler Top.It offers lightweight performance and mobility for the entry-level runner.This product is made from at least 50% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Sportswear Club
Description: The Nike Sportswear Club T-Shirt is made with our everyday cotton fabric and a classic fit, for a familiar feel right out of the bag. An embroidered Futura logo on the chest provides a signature Nike look.

name: Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece
Description: Ready for cooler weather, the Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Joggers feature an updated fit perfect for everyday wear. Roomy through the thigh, this tapered design narrows at the knee to give you a comfortable feel without losing the clean, tailored look you love. Tall ribbed cuffs complete the jogger look while a zipped pocket on the right leg provides secure small-item storage and elevates the look.

name: Nike Pro Dri-FIT
Description: The Nike Pro Dri-FIT Top helps keep you cool, dry and moving freely through your workout. Lightweight fabric with plenty of stretch is made from at least 50% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Superset
Description: The Nike Dri-FIT Superset Top feels smooth and non-restrictive as you push, pull and lift with a design that shifts the shoulder seams out of the way. Breathable fabric helps you stay cool.

name: Jordan Flight Essentials
Description: Designed with an intentionally oversized fit, this tee is ready for whatever the day brings. With a Jumpman woven patch on the chest, no one will question what you're about.

name: Paris Saint-Germain
Description: Stay warm while repping your favourite club in this PSG jacket. It's fully lined for warmth and comfort and it fastens with press studs for a sporty, streamlined look.

name: Jordan x J Balvin
Description: J Balvin remixes the classic crew to help you look good and stay warm. UV-reactive embroidered logos shimmer in the sunlight, energising any outfit.

name: Nike Dri-FIT UV
Description: From the course to the concrete and everywhere in between, the Nike Dri-FIT UV Chino Trousers keep your look fresh.The stretchy design is slightly tapered from knee to hem, creating a tailored look that's built to perform.

name: Jordan Flight Heritage 85
Description: Pay respect to the history of Flight in a tee that bridges past and present. A vintage MJ print is paired with modern graphics on soft, premium cotton.

name: Giannis Nike Dri-FIT
Description: Freakish abilities, championship pedigree. That's you on the court in the Giannis Tee. A soft feel and a relaxed fit give you room to shoot your shot and hustle back to defence.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Wild Run
Description: The tempo of your run creates music with every step. We took that rhythm and put it in visual form on this relaxed Wild Run tee. Soft, sweat-wicking fabric keeps you feeling comfortable as you set out to make more music with every mile.

name: Nike
Description: Designed with insight from trail runners around the world, the Nike Trail Socks deliver durable grip underfoot. A supportive design helps you stay running comfortably when your off-road miles become wet and rocky.

name: Golden State Warriors Icon Edition 2022/23
Description: Every team has its true colours, an unmistakable identity that sets it apart from the rest of the league. Honouring a rich hoops heritage, this Golden State Warriors jersey is inspired by what the pros wear on the hardwood, from squad details to lightweight, sweat-wicking mesh. It helps keep you dry and cool on or off the court while you rep your favourite player and the game you love.

name: Nike Everyday Lightweight
Description: Power through your workout with the Nike Everyday Lightweight Socks. Soft yarns with sweat-wicking technology help keep your feet comfortable and dry.

name: Nike Yoga Dri-FIT
Description: The soft and stretchy Nike Yoga Dri-FIT Shorts let you flow freely through your session—or anywhere else your day takes you. They bring purpose to your practice with a sweat-wicking design that is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Everyday Plus
Description: Wear them with flip-flops, wear them your AF-1s—the choice is yours. These socks are versatile enough for light workouts or your daily walk, and feature lightweight fabric and comfortable ankle support to power you through whatever your day brings.

name: Jordan Artist Series by Jacob Rochester
Description: Get ready to get noticed. This fleece hoodie features the work of artist Jacob Rochester, which tells the nostalgic story of hoops culture through bold, screen printed graphics. His imagery brings energy to a classic wardrobe staple, while a subtle Artist Series pin on the cuff legitimises your look.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Description: The Nike Dri-FIT Shorts are made to keep you moving during high-intensity training. Woven fabric stretches with every move, while vents at the hems are ideal for deep bends like Lunges and Squats. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike
Description: The Nike Shorts include an inner layer made from Nike Infinalon fabric that feels irresistibly soft and smooth while providing a gentle compressive feel as you stretch and move. The looser outer layer lets you move comfortably while staying covered. They include sweat-wicking power to help keep you dry when your training heats up.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Fleece
Description: Bring the heat with our classic Fleece Hoodie. A camo print is combined with a soft touch for warmth in cool-weather workouts. We made this one for movement so you can stretch and jump without missing a beat.

name: Nike ACG "Insects"
Description: Ready for campsites, trails and city treks alike, the ACG "Insects" tee is made from our heavyweight blended knit fabric in a roomy fit for reliable comfort no matter where your journey takes you. The colours and graphics are inspired by the natural world surrounding Spirit Lake, including all the insects that inhabit the area.

name: Nike Everyday Lightweight
Description: Power through your workout with the Nike Everyday Socks. Soft yarns with sweat-wicking technology help keep your feet comfortable and dry.

name: Nigeria
Description: Get fired up for your squad in the Nigeria Ignite T-Shirt. Proud graphics on soft knit fabric in a relaxed fit let you root for the national team in casual comfort.

name: Jordan Dri-FIT Zion
Description: Here's a hoodie you can chill in, then go straight to the gym—Zion approved. Soft fabric and sweat-wicking Dri-FIT Tech will keep you comfy no matter what you decide to do. Graphics on the chest and arms keep your look fresh.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Description: Basic doesn't mean boring. The Nike Dri-FIT Basketball Shorts have a light, loose feel with sweat-wicking technology to keep you dry. They make their mark with a large Swoosh logo cut from fabric and stitched into the side.

name: Jordan Flight MVP 85
Description: Bring the energy in a tee that reinterprets classic Jordan Brand imagery. Bold graphics make a statement on soft, relaxed cotton that you'll want to wear all day.

name: Brazil AWF
Description: Designed for unpredictable weather, this jacket is a lightweight layer for days when you want to play through the rain, but don't want to get soaked.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Player
Description: Although it's made from a stretchy performance material, the Nike Dri-FIT Player Polo pays tribute to the classic style of golf. From the chambray fabric lining the placket and hems to the repeating shield logo print that nods to the history of Nike Golf, this course-ready staple celebrates the sport's rich heritage.

name: Air Jordan x Two18
Description: Rep Detroit loud and proud with this Air Jordan x Two18 collaborative hoodie. Made from luxe, heavyweight fleece and with an all-over wash effect, you'll feel fresh all day, every day.

name: Jordan Essential Festive
Description: Who's ready for the holidays? You are, in this cosy sweatshirt. Made from plush French terry fleece with classic checked detailing, it serves nostalgic seasonal style and plenty of Jordan heritage.

name: Nike ACG
Description: This ACG tee has bold graphics inspired by the vegetation found in the Northwest's Cascade Mountain Range, particularly near Mt. Hood, Oregon. It's cut roomy from heavyweight fabric that will stand up to your biggest adventures.

name: Nike Dri-FIT ACG 'Goat Rocks'
Description: Inspired by the serene beauty of Spirit Lake, the Nike Dri-FIT ACG 'Goat Rocks' Top is made for effortless cool in warm conditions. It keeps things light and breezy with a smooth, relaxed feel against your skin. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Forward Hoodie
Description: Nike Forward catapults your classic hoodie into the future. Unlike traditional knit fabrics, Nike Forward combines multiple thin layers of select fibres for an exceptionally lightweight feel that's effortlessly warm and comfortable. Plus, this first iteration of Nike Forward reduces the carbon footprint by an average of 75% (due to the use of recycled materials, lower process-energy use, and lower material density) when used instead of our traditional knit fleece materials. A lighter future is a brighter future. Join us for the journey Forward and let's experience it together.

name: Nike ACG 'Snowgrass'
Description: Keep taking your outdoor journey to new horizons in the mid-weight feel of the Nike ACG Snowgrass Shorts. Breathable and water-repellent, they have an adjustable belt and five pockets for holding all your outdoor essentials. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester and recycled nylon fibres.

name: Nike ACG Therma-FIT 'Wolf Tree'
Description: Suit up with premium Polartec® warmth in this ACG Therma-FIT 'Wolf Tree' Hoodie. Designed to be worn as a layering piece or on its own, this pullover has a hood so you can keep the elements at bay.

name: Nike ACG
Description: Made from soft blended fabric for a comfy feel, this long-sleeve Nike ACG tee features our "Lungs" logo and ACG graphics for a classic finish. Plus, sweat-wicking fabric works to help you stay dry when you're out putting your lungs to the test.

name: Nike ACG
Description: This tee reminds us to consider the impact we make with every action we take. Cut roomy from heavyweight fabric that will stand up to your biggest adventures, it features a bold topographical shot of Mt. Hood on the back.

name: Nike ACG 'Sunfarer'
Description: Overcome whatever obstacle you find around the next bend in the trail in these versatile hiking trousers. They're made from stretchy, lightweight fabric that helps shed water for easy mobility and wetness protection. Targeted abrasion resistance and cooling zones are based on Nike athlete data to help you stay comfortable while you stay the course.

name: Nike ACG "Sun Farer"
Description: Don't let a little cold air stop you from exploring. The Nike ACG "Sun Farer" Jacket keeps the elements at bay while you keep going. It's loose and roomy with a design geared for all-round mobility so you stay moving when adventure takes you off the beaten path. Extra coverage courtesy of a hood can be packed away when the wet weather disappears. Layer up over a base and midlayer for total comfort. This product is made with at least 75% recycled nylon fibres.

name: Nike ACG Polartec® 'Wolf Tree'
Description: Wet weather doesn't mean you have to stop exploring. Stay warm in our design inspired by Oregon's Smith Rock. Remarkably soft fabric, made from 100% recycled polyester fibres, helps you stay warm when temperatures begin to drop. Zipped storage keeps your essentials close.

name: Nike Challenger
Description: The iconic Nike Challenger Shorts deliver sweat-wicking comfort for your run. They offer the versatility and breathability you want from everyday shorts. This product is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Jordan Sport Dri-FIT
Description: The Jordan Sport Dri-FIT Shorts strike a balance between performance and street style. Made from sweat-wicking fabric, they're light, loose and breathable to help you stay cool and comfortable.

name: Nike SB Kearny
Description: Made from durable Ripstop fabric, the Nike SB Kearny Cargo Trousers are built to last. The classic cargo design doesn't skimp on storage—with 6 pockets, you'll have plenty of places to keep your essentials secure while you skate.

name: Jordan Dri-FIT Sport
Description: Zip up, head out and stay fresh in this sleek hoodie. Its full-length zip extends up to the hood, keeping wind and chill at bay. Meanwhile, sweat-wicking Dri-FIT Technology ups the versatility, making this your go-to layer for everything from workouts to hangouts.

name: Jordan Brand Sorry
Description: Sorry, not sorry—Rose City, '92 just wasn't your year. This relaxed tee highlights what went down in the legendary season that led to MJ winning his first back-to-back championships. Printed graphics give a playful nod to the joys and sorrow of pro ball.

name: Jordan x Wordmark
Description: Keep it simple and stylish. Made from quality, heavyweight cotton with minimal branding, this tee is a subtle standout.

name: Nike Sportswear Air
Description: The Nike Air collection pays tribute to the sneakers that helped shape the Swoosh brand over the decades. These French terry trousers are made from French terry fabric for soft warmth and comfort that lasts. Nike Air graphics, piping down the seams and soft elastic trims elevate the finish. Pair them up with your favourite "Airs" for a clean, city-ready look.

name: Croatia 2022/23 Stadium Home
Description: Like other shirts from our Stadium collection, this one pairs replica design details with sweat-wicking fabric to give you a game-ready look inspired by your favourite team.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Victory
Description: Crafted from breathable, sweat-wicking fabric that's made from 100% recycled polyester fibres, the Nike Dri-FIT Victory Polo puts a modern spin on golf performance. The ribbed collar and the buttons on the placket were also made using recycled materials.

name: Paris Saint-Germain 2022/23 Stadium Away
Description: Like other shirts from our Stadium collection, this one pairs replica design details with sweat-wicking fabric to give you a game-ready look inspired by your favourite team. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Brazil Strike
Category: Men's Nike Dri-FIT Knit Football Shorts
Description: The Brazil Strike Shorts have design details specifically tailored for football's rising stars. A slim, streamlined fit ensures that nothing comes between you and the ball, and sweat-wicking fabric helps keep you cool and composed while fine-tuning your skills.

name: Paris Saint-Germain
Description: Rep your favourite club in crisp, lightweight comfort. These woven pants are water-repellent, relaxed and threaded through with Jordan DNA and premier Paris identity.

name: Brooklyn Nets Icon Edition 2022/23
Description: Every team has its true colours, an unmistakable identity that sets it apart from the rest of the league. Honouring a rich hoops heritage, this Brooklyn Nets jersey is inspired by what the pros wear on the hardwood, from squad details to lightweight, sweat-wicking mesh. It helps keep you dry and cool on or off the court while you rep your favourite player and the game you love.

name: Jordan 23 Engineered
Description: Take your look to the next level with trousers from 23 Engineered. Made from lightweight, water-repellent material, they feature zip pockets and a belted waist for on-the-go functionality. It's not all about utility, though—a subtle grid pattern adds visual interest and the slightly cropped hem lets you show off your favourite kicks.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Standard Issue
Description: The sweat-wicking Standard Issue Jersey combines the feel of performance with a classic look for beyond the court. It's a soft, reversible staple made to be ready-to-go right out of your gym bag. Wear it as a top layer or only layer for a smooth, breathable feel.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Description: Move comfortably on and off the course in the Nike Dri-FIT Shorts. Stretchy fabric lets you line up your putts without restriction and a tacky waistband helps keep your shirt tucked in while you bend and swing.

name: Nike Solo Swoosh
Description: A classic never goes out of style.Heavyweight fabric is mixed with a loose fit for a premium look and feel.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Challenger
Description: The Nike Dri-FIT Challenger Trousers are made from 100% recycled polyester fibres so you can feel good in more ways than one. Smooth, light fabric with sweat-wicking technology helps you stay dry and comfortable. Snap-button pockets keep your gear close.

name: Jordan Essentials
Description: Gear up, Jumpman style. These relaxed shorts are lightweight, durable and comfortable—throw 'em on and focus on your game.

name: Nike Multiplier
Description: The Nike Multiplier Running Ankle Socks feature sweat-wicking fabric. An arch band at the midfoot offers a comfortable, close fit ideal for different types of runs.

name: Nike Pro Dri-FIT
Description: The Nike Pro Dri-FIT Top hugs you in lightweight fabric with breathability built into high-heat zones to help keep you cool and dry from warm-ups to cool-downs. Stretchy fabric made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres comes in a tight fit that easily layers under other tops.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Academy
Description: The Nike Dri-FIT Academy Shorts refuse to let sweat slow you down.Slightly stretchy fabric moves sweat off your skin, so you can focus on playing your best. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Chelsea F.C. 2022/23 Stadium Away
Description: Like other shirts from our Stadium collection, this one pairs replica design details with sweat-wicking fabric to give you a game-ready look inspired by your favourite team. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Sportswear
Description: The Nike Sportswear Utility Cargo Trousers are outfitted with the storage and comfort that a day on your feet demands. Cargo pockets and a flap back pocket make sure your phone, keys and other essentials are stored safely whether you're on the trail or commuting from work. A roomy, stylish fit helps you move without distraction and look your best.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Description: The Nike Dri-FIT Team Training Trousers are lightweight, flexible and designed to help you stay dry through your entire workout. Soft woven fabric feels smooth against your skin and the tapered legs are designed to help you move through your drills and lifts without distractions. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Brazil 2022/23 Stadium Away
Description: Our "garra" is never done. Like other shirts from our Stadium collection, this one pairs replica design details with sweat-wicking fabric to give you a game-ready look inspired by your favourite team.

name: Zion Sneaker School
Description: Show some love for Zion with this all-cotton tee. With a relaxed fit and bold graphics, it's got your back (literally).

name: Nike
Description: Bring your game with warm, summery vibes over a relaxed-feeling tee. That tropical Swoosh you wear is a sign you're on basketball island, a look inspired by seaside tournaments where a round of five-on-five is your idea of the perfect trip.

name: Netherlands 2022/23 Stadium Home
Description: Oranje pride is never done. Like other shirts from our Stadium collection, this one pairs replica design details with sweat-wicking fabric to give you a game-ready look inspired by your favourite team.

name: Nike
Description: Made from heavyweight cotton for a premium, structured feel, this roomy-fitting T-shirt gives you some extra space through the shoulders, chest and body for ease of movement.

name: Nike Sportswear
Description: From the street to the stage, sometimes a comfy base layer is all you need. The familiar feel of soft cotton—cut to fit loose—lets you express yourself in comfort while a chain-inspired Swoosh design adds bold appeal perfect for serving original style on and off the dance floor.

name: Nike Sportswear
Description: Whether you're looking for an adventure out of town or just running some errands, these light and airy shorts are the perfect companion. Their smooth woven fabric and breathable mesh liner help you stay cool and comfortable on warmer days while a grommet in the back pocket allows water to drain out easily.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Flex
Description: The Nike Flex Yoga Trousers give you a lightweight, comfortable layer for the mat. Soft, flexible fabric stretches around the waist and ankles to keep them in place as you bend and stretch through your practice. This product is made from at least 50% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Description: With a 3/4 design that falls below the knee, these trousers provide a distraction-free fit while you train and compete. The soft, stretch-woven fabric flexes with you while you move and has our sweat-wicking tech built in to keep you dry.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Run Division Pinnacle
Description: Suit up in soft comfort in our sweat-wicking Run Division Top. It's lightweight yet insulating for those cool weather runs when you need a little extra warmth to keep you going.

name: Nike Sportswear Air
Description: The Nike Air collection pays tribute to the sneakers that helped shape the Swoosh brand over the decades. These French terry shorts are made from French terry fabric for soft warmth and comfort that lasts. Nike Air printed graphics, piping down the seams and a soft elastic waist elevate the finish. Pair them up with your favourite "Airs" for a clean, city-ready look.

name: Nike Sportswear Circa
Description: This jacket takes inspiration from the clothing worn during the running boom of the 1970s while offering the modern performance you deserve. Water-repellent and lined with mesh, it's designed to keep you dry and comfortable through whatever your day holds. Sneaky details like the vented back and elastic binding at the cuffs and hem let you experience a piece of running's journey while looking forward to the road ahead.

name: Jordan Dri-FIT Sport BC
Description: Go for the gold in shorts inspired by one of MJ's most legendary looks. A hand-drawn design riffs on the head-to-toe AJ7 print he wore in Barcelona during the 1992 Summer Games. They're built with sweat-wicking Dri-FIT Technology and breathable mesh that's 100% recycled, so you can take on the world in comfort.

name: Tottenham Hotspur 2022/23 Stadium Away
Description: Like other shirts from our Stadium collection, this one pairs replica design details with sweat-wicking fabric to give you a game-ready look inspired by your favourite team. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Tiger Woods 'Frank'
Description: Frank's back. The head cover to Tiger's driver gets the spotlight over this super-soft and comfortable tee.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Flex
Category: Men's 9" (23cm approx.) Woven Camo Fitness Shorts
Description: High-intensity trainings are all about movement. Flex freely in these sweat-wicking shorts, made from stretchy fabric that lets you give your all without holding back.

name: Nike Dri-FIT DNA
Description: Take care of the future like you take care of the ball in the Nike Dri-FIT DNA Shorts. Made from at least 75% recycled polyester, they offer light, breathable fabric that's tailored for the game.

name: Nike F.C. Repel
Description: These lightweight pants keep it cool and dry for comfort beyond the pitch. We made them with a tapered fit and a water-repellent finish so you have the look of streetwear with the comfort of game-ready gear.

name: Nike Sportswear Max90
Description: Made from our soft midweight cotton fabric in a roomy fit for casual wear, this Nike tee highlights the good vibes that are out there in our world. Pull it on, go find a rainbow and have a Nike day.

name: Jordan x Zion
Description: Believe it! Zion is an anime super-fan, and now you can rep his passion with this Jordan x Zion tee. Flex his favourite show on soft and lightweight cotton, equally perfect for workouts or hangouts.

name: Nike Run Division Miler
Description: What's a little rain when you're hitting the tarmac in our Run Division Jacket? Made from stretchy, water-repellent fabric, it's designed to help you stay dry and get the most from your stride. Plus, we added a reflective-design print made to look like a city grid in honour of those who bring their workout to the urban landscape.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Run Division Challenger
Description: Hit the pavement on your daily run in our sweat-wicking Run Division Challenger Shorts. They're light and airy, with plenty of storage for your keys and phone. Plus, they have an internal liner for the support you need to go the extra mile. This product is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Jordan Jumpman
Description: Rise and shine in this classic tee from Jordan Brand. Made from soft, comfortable cotton, it features a clean, classic Jumpman that's embroidered on the chest.

name: Nike Sportswear Everyday Essential
Description: Put your best foot forward with the Nike Sportswear Everyday Essential Socks. Made from soft, stretchy fabric and designed for daily wear, they're durable, breathable and extra comfortable. This product is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Sportswear
Description: Look into your crystal ball, and you will see our soft cotton tee with a relaxed fit. The graphic is inspired by fantasy and magic, and sets you up for odysseys unknown.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Run Division Challenger
Description: When every run is a push to feel great, our sweat-wicking Challenger Shorts are there to take you through the finish. We tuned the Run Division version to provide smooth support with reflective design to help keep you comfortable while you strive for better.

name: LeBron
Description: We made the water-repellent LeBron Utility Jacket with heavyweight fabric and insulation so you can stay at your best when the temperature goes down. The graphics nod to 20 years of greatness on the court for LeBron, pushing his game further every year in a chess match with father time.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Phenom Elite
Description: Step freely throughout your run in our lightweight Phenom Elite Trousers. We know you're out there giving your all, so we keep you feeling comfortable with stretchy, sweat-wicking fabric. Plus, there's pockets for everything from your phone to your keys.

name: Nike Sportswear Club+
Description: Zip into our Club+ Woven Bomber Jacket and get after your day. The classic bomber style has an acid-washed finish for a vintage, worn-in look. Soft cotton, clean lines and a casual cut make it the perfect choice for daily wear.

name: Nike Pro Dri-FIT Flex Vent Max
Description: Made from lightweight, stretchy fabric, the Nike Pro Flex Shorts move with your body through your most intense workouts. An elastic, fold-over waistband lets you easily adjust your fit and the sweat-wicking technology helps you stay dry, so you can zero in on the challenges ahead. This product is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike
Description: A comfy tee for the cold-blooded hooper shooting 3-pointers. Soft and roomy, it gives you enough room to move on and off the court.

name: Paris Saint-Germain
Description: Get comfortable without losing your cool in these all-day versatile Jordan x PSG shorts. They're made from breathable mesh with zip pockets for the essentials. Print and label details highlight our ongoing collaboration with your favourite football club.

name: Nike Dri-FIT ADV AeroSwift
Description: Your hard work has got you to the starting line. Let the Nike Dri-FIT ADV AeroSwift Tights take you to the finish. Soft and smooth, with a lightweight, secure feel, these tights are geared to help you reach your personal best. This product is made with at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Air Jordan x Shelflife
Description: Jordan and South Africa's coveted sneaker shop Shelflife come together on this soft, everyday tee. It's made with an all-over wash for a perfectly faded look, and the graphic on the back pays homage to the store's original stained glass window.

name: Brazil
Category: Men's Nike Dri-FIT Woven Football Shorts
Description: From a quick workout to an impromptu swim, the Brasil Shorts are ready for whatever adventures come your way. Sweat-wicking technology and a hem that hits above the knee help keep you moving comfortably.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Description: Your off-road adventure gets a little more comfortable with this soft, relaxed tee. The fabric wicks moisture away from your body so the top won't stick to you when your trail run heats up.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Description: Throw it back to the '90s with the grunge-inspired look of our sweat-wicking jersey. We made this one with smooth mesh and a graphic that nods to the anarchic spirit of the decade.

name: Nike Sportswear Tech Pack
Description: We gave this lifestyle top a dose of high-performance tech for your city adventures. The knit fabric wicks sweat to help you stay dry, while the breathable, woven-in all-over floral pattern keeps your seasonal look fresh and always in bloom.

name: Nike ACG
Description: Breathe in that fresh air with this spacious, soft tee. It feels like a classic, with a slightly baggy fit. And when you're out enjoying the great outdoors, the lung-shaped graphic reminds you to stop, breathe and take in the scenery. This product is made from 100% sustainable materials, using a blend of both recycled polyester and organic cotton fibres. The blend is at least 10% recycled fibres or at least 10% organic cotton fibres.

name: Air Jordan Wordmark
Description: Your favourite shorts have some new competition. Made from soft, heavyweight fleece, this pair looks classic but feels luxe. An all-over wash effect adds a perfectly faded vintage aesthetic.

name: The Nike Polo
Description: This isn't your average polo—it's The Nike Polo. Every detail from its innovative, sweat-wicking fabric to the hints of orange that nod to Nike's original shoebox, has been thoughtfully crafted to meet the needs of the everyday you. The result is a street-ready style that looks at home on the course, the court and everywhere else.

name: Nike SB
Description: Add this cardigan to your line-up and let its casual, unplugged vibes deliver easy comfort and lightweight warmth. Just like the cardigans hanging at the back of your parents' wardrobe, this simple, spacious look is ready to dress up or down.

name: Air Jordan x Two18
Description: Rep your Midwest pride with this collaborative tee celebrating Detroit's Two18 sneaker boutique. The all-over wash effect gives a perfectly faded look, while subtle branding and an original screen print add a luxe level of detail.

name: Nike Sportswear Air
Description: The Nike Air collection celebrates the legendary sneakers that helped shape the Swoosh brand over the decades. This French terry crew is made from heavy fleece fabric for soft warmth and comfort that lasts. A Nike Air rubber graphic printed on the chest and cover-stitch piping down the seams elevate the finish.

name: Nike
Description: Take your best shot with the soft feel of this relaxed tee. We looked to the '90s for inspiration, coming back with a graphic that nods to the music legends of the era.

name: Jordan Sport Dri-FIT
Description: Bring street style and Jordan heritage to the court. These lightweight shorts are made from breathable mesh in a classic, relaxed silhouette. With sweat-wicking Dri-FIT Technology and the iconic Diamond design, they'll keep you looking and feeling fresh all day.

name: Los Angeles Lakers Courtside Max 90
Description: Show your hoops allegiance in this loose-fitting Los Angeles Lakers T-shirt. Soft knit fabric with a proud team print front and centre lets everyone know who your squad is, whether you're courtside or streetside.

name: Nike Challenger
Description: Stretch your legs on the road to a better you. Our Challenger Shorts keep you moving freely and feeling good with soft, breathable fabric. name: Milwaukee Bucks City Edition

name: Nike Dri-FIT ADV A.P.S.

Shorts to be worn at any time, so you're ready for that high-intensity training at a moment's notice. They're stretchy and breathable so you can get through your reps with ease. Need to go for a quick swim? We added holes in the pockets to help water drain out if you're in the mood for some laps in the pool.

name: Nike ACG Storm-FIT ADV 'Cascade Rains'
Description: The Cascade Mountain Range ensures that the western part of the Pacific Northwest gets a lot of rain. That rain is what makes our climate so beautiful, but it also can make being in that environment difficult. We've created Storm-FIT ADV tech to keep you dry and comfortable through it all. The jacket is entirely seam-sealed and paired with water-resistant zips to keep the rain from leaking in. That way, you can enjoy your time exploring the wilderness no matter what the weather throws your way.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Stride
Description: The Nike Dri-FIT Stride Shorts have a lightweight feel designed for unrestricted movement. They're smooth to the touch—made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres—with extra breathability at the upper back. Need to take a phone along? They've got a pocket at the back geared just for your device. There's even gusseted side pockets that help keep your keys or card from falling out.

Description: Strive for greatness—and comfort—in this long-sleeve tee. It feels smooth, like an old favourite, with a roomy feel that won't get in your way.

Description: The Nike AeroSwift Shorts keep you ready for your race.Lightweight and breathable, they have a convenient pocket for smaller items. This product is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Dri-FIT D.Y.E.
Description: Get your workout going and your neurons firing in these sweat-wicking shorts. We made these to help you get the most out of your reps with soft, breathable fabric. That graphic you see is based off your brain's reaction to exercise and the joy it releases with every step, push and lunge.

name: FFF 2022/23 Stadium Home
Description: Like other shorts from our Stadium collection, these pair replica design details with sweat-wicking fabric to give you a match-ready look inspired by your favourite team.

name: Paris Saint-Germain Strike
Category: Men's Nike Dri-FIT Short-Sleeve Football Top
Description: The Paris Saint-Germain Strike Top has design details specifically tailored for football's rising stars. A slim, streamlined fit ensures that nothing comes between you and the ball, and sweat-wicking fabric helps keep you cool and composed while fine-tuning your skills. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Description: Bring the heat in this sweat-wicking tee with a relaxed feel that won't bunch up when you hit your reps.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Description: Your off-road adventure gets a little more comfortable with this relaxed and soft tee. The fabric wicks sweat, so the top won't cling to you when your trail run heats up.

name: New Orleans Pelicans Icon Edition 2022/23
Description: Every team has its true colours, an unmistakable identity that sets it apart from the rest of the league. Honouring a rich hoops heritage, this New Orleans Pelicans jersey is inspired by what the pros wear on the hardwood, from squad details to lightweight, sweat-wicking mesh. It helps keep you dry and cool on or off the court while you rep your favourite player and the game you love.

name: Nike Sportswear
Description: The Nike Sportswear T-Shirt is made from our everyday cotton and has a classic fit for a smooth, familiar feel. Printed graphics on the chest and back bring new life to the Futura logo.

name: Nike Spark Lightweight
Description: The Nike Spark Lightweight Socks have a thin design with sweat-wicking technology and mesh fabric for a dry and cool experience. Extra yarn in the footbed and ankle provides subtle cushioning, giving you soft support with every step. Reflective design elements are placed in key areas, making this sock stand out from previous versions.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Giannis
Description: With freakish abilities and a championship mindset, Giannis brings an otherworldly skill set to the basketball court. Celebrate the MVP in this embossed mesh jersey. It feels soft and breathable, with sweat-wicking technology so you stay comfortable on the court and beyond.

name: Nike Sportswear
Description: The Nike Sportswear Shorts elevate a warm-weather staple with water-resistant seersucker. Lined with mesh, the lightweight fabric helps you stay cool and dry no matter what weather.

name: Jordan Essentials
Description: Get moving in trousers that flex with you. This relaxed pair is made from lightweight, stretch-woven fabric textured with suede-like softness.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Rise 365
Description: A lightweight favourite returns with more breathability. The Nike Dri-FIT 365 Top is made using runner-informed data for cooling in areas where you need it. It has the same soft feel you've come to expect, with design details that nod to the iconic Nike chevron. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: NikeCourt Dri-FIT ADV Slam
Description: Rally to greatness in our innovative Slam Polo. The iconic tennis heroes of the past inspired us to reinvent the future, with a stretchy, breathable fabric that helps you perform at the highest levels of play. Your swing needs to be at its best, so we made sure the sleeve seams are moved forwards, keeping your arms free as you slice and smash for the win.

name: Nike Yoga Therma-FIT
Description: The Nike Yoga Pants are made from super-soft fleece for warmth and comfort. The tapered legs, elastic waistband and roomy gusset let you move freely and without distraction while you shift positions and poses.

name: Nike Dri-FIT ADV Vapor
Description: Let our Engineered Vapor Polo help keep you cool, focused and comfortable through your swing. We made this one with fabric from some of our favourite running and training gear, adding a breathable front and smooth feel—so you stay fresh as you stare down the course.

name: Kevin Durant Nets
Description: Pay tribute to your favourite player and their skills on the hardwood in this MVP jersey. Wear their name and number with pride while celebrating the NBA's 75th anniversary with diamond-themed details. Lightweight, breathable fabric wicks sweat to help you stay dry and cool while you're repping this pro.

name: Nike Sportswear Sport Essentials
Description: Whether you're running to the nearest food truck or diving into your favourite swimming hole, the Nike Sportswear Sport Essentials Lined Flow Shorts are a good idea. Lined for comfort, the smooth woven fabric is lightweight and lends itself to adventures of all kinds.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Run Division
Description: Bring some heat to the city streets in our Run Division Tee. Throw it on before your miles and feel the difference with its sweat-wicking, soft cotton-blend fabric.

name: Nike ACG
Description: Built to sustain the journey from the trailhead to your destination and then some, these trail shorts pack a lot of function into a lightweight, do-it-all solution. Woven fabric is soft, stretchy and water-repellent. They're also equipped with lightweight webbing and zip utility pockets for your trail essentials, making these your go-to trail shorts when you start itching to get outdoors.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Description: Start your day off right in the Nike Dri-FIT T-Shirt. It's soft and lightweight, with sweat-wicking technology to help you stay comfortable.

name: Nike Stride D.Y.E.
Description: Built for unrestricted movement, these lightweight Stride Shorts help keep your momentum going with an all-over neuron print tracing the pathways in your brain that release endorphins as the miles tick by. It's a celebration of you and the joy of the run.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Category: Men's 9" (23cm approx.) Woven Graphic Fitness Shorts
Description: Push through your limit during high-intensity training with these Dri-FIT Shorts. Flexible fabric stretches with your every move, letting you lift, pull and push freely. A modernised Swoosh graphic gets you mentally ready to take your workout to new horizons.

name: LeBron
Description: Strive for greatness—and comfort—in this long-sleeve tee. It feels smooth, like an old favourite, with a roomy feel that won't get in your way.

name: Nike Air
Description: The Nike Sportswear T-Shirt is made from our everyday cotton and has a classic fit for a smooth, familiar feel. Printed graphics on the front and back combine logos new and classic for a fresh look ready to pair with your favourite sneakers.

name: Nike Air
Description: The Nike Air collection pays tribute to the legendary sneakers that helped shape the Swoosh brand over the decades. This knit jacket gives you a full-zip, Air-infused top to pair up with your favourite sneakers and hit the city looking fresh.

name: Rui
Description: Rep Rui Hachimura, the first-ever Japanese player to be picked in Round 1 of the NBA Draft. With stylised graphics printed on a classic soft tee, who's to say you wont wear this every day?

name: Nike SB
Description: Made from a soft mid-weight cotton and with reinforced stitching, this woven top is durable enough for daily riding and comfortable enough to wear anywhere. The soft fabric feels smooth against your skin, yet structured enough to withstand the woes of learning and earning that new trick.

name: Brooklyn Nets Courtside
Description: Take the court in the breathable comfort of these lightweight Brooklyn Nets shorts. With squad colours and logo details on a loose-fitting design, they show your team allegiance while letting you move freely as you score baskets.

name: Nike Air
Description: Made from our mid-weight cotton in a relaxed fit for casual, everyday wear, this long-sleeve has printed graphics on the left side of the chest and the sleeve that give a nod to the iconic Nike Air franchise.

name: Nike AeroSwift
Description: The Nike AeroSwift Shorts keep you ready for your race with a lightweight design.Sweat-wicking technology and a ventilated waistband help keep you dry and cool on the go.This product is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

Description: These mesh shorts celebrate classic above-the-knee basketball shorts with twill-taped trims and double-stitched details, nodding to the ankle breakers and shot makers from back in the day. This timeless crossover keeps your game fresh, no matter where you take it.

name: Nike Sportswear
Description: Thanks to its lightweight cotton fabric and classic fit, the Nike Sportswear T-Shirt is as easy to love as fresh produce and sneakers.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Stride
Description: Flex your speed, embrace the momentum. The Nike Dri-FIT Stride Shorts have a lightweight feel—made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres—designed for unrestricted movement. They're smooth to the touch, with extra breathability at the upper back. Need to take a phone along? We've got a pocket at the back geared just for your device.

name: LeBron
Description: LeBron's motto is "Strive for Greatness" and this soft fleece hoodie invites you to bring that message with you wherever you go. It's built with an extra roomy fit for dependable warmth, while graphics on the back celebrate The King's illustrious career that's still going strong.

name: Nike Sportswear Premium Essentials
Description: The Nike Sportswear Long-Sleeve T-Shirt has a loose fit for a carefree, comfortable look. Its heavyweight organic cotton fabric feels thick and soft. A subtle Futura logo at the centre of the front of the T-Shirt offers a signature Nike look while a set-on collar ensures a clean, comfortable fit. This product is made from at least 75% organic cotton fibres.

name: Nike Sportswear
Description: Clean lines and an oversized fit make the Nike Sportswear Jacket an invaluable styling piece. Made from water-resistant seersucker, it's a lightweight layer you can count on to keep you dry in unexpected showers and looking your best in the sunshine.

name: LeBron
Description: Time to take on the cool with the warm feel of our LeBron Trousers. We're celebrating 20 years of LeBron on the court, with chess and time piece graphics honouring his mind for the game and his battle to keep his body pristine through the rigours of age. Those embroidered graphics are over a heavyweight fleece feel that'll help keep you comfortable in cold conditions.

Description: The Nike Multiplier No-Show Socks feature sweat-wicking fabric. An arch band in the midfoot offers a comfortable, close fit ideal for different types of training.

Description: Visualise the art of Flight in this Jumpman tee. It's made from soft cotton with an easy, relaxed fit.

name: Paris Saint-Germain
Description: Icons unite in the Jordan x Paris Saint-Germain collab tee. It's made from structured heavyweight cotton with dropped shoulders and an easy, relaxed fit.

name: Nike Sportswear Modern Essentials
Description: The Nike Sportswear Modern Essentials Shorts are made from a lightweight sweat-wicking woven fabric to help keep you cool and comfortable. An elastic waistband and comfortable fit that hits at the mid-thigh make them an ideal option for everyday wear.

name: Liverpool F.C.
Category: Men's Nike Dri-FIT Pre-Match Football Top
Description: The Liverpool F.C. Top gives you the same look as your favourite players. Sweat-wicking technology is lightweight and breathable to help keep you dry while you're warming up for the match. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Jordan Air
Description: This all-cotton Jordan tee features a minimal, embroidered graphic across the chest. A relaxed fit and monochromatic look make it an easy choice.

name: Nike Yoga Dri-FIT
Description: The Nike Yoga Top is made from lightweight knit fabric for a soft, smooth feel against your skin. Sweat-wicking technology will help keep you dry, so you can stay comfortable and focused on your practice. And it's mindfully made from at least 50% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Jordan x J Balvin
Description: Bold, bright and full of light

name: Nike Pro Dri-FIT Vent Max
Description: Made from soft, stretchy fabric, the Nike Vent Max Trousers help you move freely before, during and after your workout. A tapered design reduces distractions, so you can focus on powering through your lifts and drills. And, they're mindfully made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Sportswear
colors: Dark Marina Blue/Yellow Ochre/Dark Marina BlueStyle
Description: Fill your bag with comfort in this loose-fitting cotton tee. A roomy feel, soft cotton and fresh graphics take you from the checkout queue to the streets in style that's ready for the picking.

name: Nike
Description: Nike Basketball takes it back to the grunge era in our premium shorts. They combine a roomy fit and a length that hits above the knee with performance feel for beyond the court. A leopard print shows off your '90s spirit.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Flex
Description: Keep moving during your high-intensity workout in our Flex Woven Shorts. We added a bold take on the Swoosh logo, while still maintaining the stretch you need to go for every lunge or squat.

name: Jordan Flight Essentials
Description: Big 'n' baggy for comfort and style. This super-soft tee features longer sleeves and dropped shoulders. Combined with a minimal Jumpman woven chest patch, you're lookin' n-i-c-e.

name: Nike ACG Therma-FIT ADV 'Rope de Dope'
Description: Cold conditions are just an invitation for new discovery. Our ACG Therma-FIT ADV 'Rope De Dope' Gilet combines innovative technology with an insulated design for comfort tailored to all conditions. Best of all, it packs down small so you can stow it in a pocket when the trail heats up.

name: Giannis Nike Dri-FIT
Description: Suit up in sweat-wicking mesh shorts with prints inspired by the 9th wonder of the world—Giannis. Channel his championship mentality with a smooth, easy feel that lets you move up the court and beyond with ease.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Stride Run Division
Description: Transition from work to route and maintain your pace in the lightweight feel of our Run Division Shorts. A 2-in-1 design means you have the support of tights with the breathable, free-flowing feel of your favourite shorts.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Wild Run Challenger
Description: The wild beckons. Answer the call in the Nike Challenger Wild Run Shorts. They feature the same sweat-wicking fabric and articulated brief you love with details highlighting the tempo of your feet as they hit their stride. Graphics nod to running as music, with the tempo of your feet, serving as the beat. This product is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Korea AWF
Description: Stand proudly with your team as an all-weather fan in the Korea Jacket. Soft fleece and a water-repellent finish help keep you dry and warm when you're cheering on your squad in cool, wet conditions.

name: Nike Dri-FIT ADV A.P.S.
Description: Ready for anything, at any time. That's where we started with the Axis Performance System (A.P.S.) Recovery Top. It's a compressive base layer with a smooth, stretchy feel that keeps you going after your high-intensity workout has ended. Plus, it's powered by advanced sweat-wicking technology, so you stay comfortable even when your workout turns up the heat.

name: Nike ACG
Description: Loose, roomy, outdoor ready.The Nike ACG T-Shirt keeps things comfy with a graphic repping All Conditions Gear. This product is made from 100% sustainable materials, using a blend of both recycled polyester and organic cotton fibres.The blend is at least 10% recycled fibres or at least 10% organic cotton fibres.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Q5
Description: This sweat-wicking top helps keep you cool, dry and comfortable through all your workouts—this time with a bold take on the Swoosh logo. It brings that soft, lightweight feel to help you focus on your exercise routine.

name: Nike Sportswear
Description: This NSW tee is made with our everyday cotton fabric and a classic fit for a familiar feel straight out of the bag. Our heatwave graphics add a dose of peace, unity and drip to your street-ready style.

name: Jordan x J Balvin
Description: Your favourite Jordan Brand shorts get a J Balvin remix with UV-reactive screen prints that shift colours when you step out on a sunny day. They're great for warm summer nights, too—saturated with bright colours, they'll stand out from the court to the dance floor.

name: Korea 2022/23 Match Home
Category: Men's Nike Dri-FIT ADV Football Shirt
Description: Our Match collection pairs authentic design details with lightweight, quick-drying technology to help keep the world's biggest football stars cool and comfortable on the pitch.

name: Lakers Icon Edition 2020
Description: The Icon Edition jersey represents the franchise's rich heritage and iconic identity, expressed through the team's bold colours. The Nike NBA Icon Edition Swingman Jersey of the Los Angeles Lakers is inspired by what the pros wear. Premium double-knit fabric has a classic jersey construction and a fit that looks good from all angles. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike
Description: Our Nike F.C. Tee brings a performance feel out of the stadium. It has the soft sensation you want from a favourite, with graphics honouring the biggest tournament in football.

name: Jordan Essential
Description: Gear up in everyday comfort. Made from soft fleece in a relaxed fit, these shorts feature an embroidered Jumpman logo that elevates a heritage style.

name: Nike Sportswear
Description: Rebel against cold, dreary days with the Nike Sportswear Pullover Hoodie. Made from French terry fabric, its versatile warmth is perfect for cool-weather layering. The printed graphics bring a sense of joy and positivity that can't help but make you smile.

name: Nike Sportswear Air
Description: The Nike Air collection pays tribute to the legendary sneakers that helped shape the Swoosh brand over the decades. These knit trousers give you a comfy base to pair up with your favourite Air sneakers for a fresh, city-ready look.

name: Nike Yoga Dri-FIT
Description: The Nike Yoga Tank is made from lightweight knit fabric for a soft, smooth feel against your skin. Sweat-wicking technology helps keep you dry, so you can stay comfortable and focused on your practice. And it's mindfully made from at least 50% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike ACG "Hike Box"
Description: This one's for the outdoor enthusiast who dreams of mountain trails and forest frolics even when they're stuck in traffic or behind a desk. When you pull this on, you'll know from the sweat-wicking fabric and roomy, movement-friendly fit that it's time to head into the great outdoors.

name: Jordan Flight Heritage '85
Description: Take flight in this new graphic tee featuring custom artwork from Joe Perez. Made from structured cotton with a relaxed fit, it's made to wear all day long.

name: Charlotte Hornets Icon Edition 2022/23
Description: Every team has its true colours, an unmistakable identity that sets it apart from the rest of the league. Honouring a rich hoops heritage, this Charlotte Hornets jersey is inspired by what the pros wear on the hardwood, from squad details to lightweight, sweat-wicking mesh. It helps keep you dry and cool on or off the court while you rep your favourite player and the game you love.

name: Nike Dri-FIT UV
Description: From the course to the concrete and everywhere in between, the Nike Dri-FIT UV Chino Shorts keep your look fresh. Stretchy fabric and multiple pockets create a casual, comfortable fit that's built to perform at the highest levels of play.

name: Nike Sportswear Sport Essentials+
Description: More than a direct descendant, the Nike Sportswear Windrunner Windbreaker is made to look and feel just like the original Windrunner from 1978. It has a breathable mesh lining, ribbed cuffs and the iconic chevron on the chest. A mix of smooth and puffy printed logos elevates the look.

name: Netherlands 2022/23 Stadium Away
Description: Oranje pride is never done. Like other shirts from our Stadium collection, this one pairs replica design details with sweat-wicking fabric to give you a game-ready look inspired by your favourite team.

name: NikeCourt Dri-FIT Victory
Description: Crafted from soft fabric with plenty of stretch, the NikeCourt Dri-FIT Victory Top keeps you comfortable and focused on the win.The updated design blends the feel of raglan sleeves with the look of traditional polo sleeves—providing more room to move.This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Sportswear
Description: Designed with our classic fit and everyday cotton fabric, the Nike Sportswear T-Shirt has a soft, familiar feel perfect for everyday wear. All-over printed graphics bring energy to your look.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Flex
Description: Get the most out of your workout in shorts built for dynamic moves. Flexible fabric powered by sweat-wicking technology helps keep you cool and comfortable while side-splits in the hem give you room to lunge and squat. A simple but functional design keeps distractions to a minimum, letting you focus on your training.

name: Los Angeles Lakers Courtside
Description: Take the court in the breathable comfort of these lightweight Los Angeles Lakers shorts. With squad colours and logo details on a loose-fitting design, they show your team allegiance while letting you move freely as you score baskets.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Player
Description: A timeless essential remade for modern golf, the Nike Dri-FIT Player Polo blends the look and feel of a classic polo with the incredible performance of sweat-wicking fabric. Subtle stripes and elevated trim details—like chambray linings and pearlised buttons—finish the look.

name: Jordan x Zion
Description: Zion is a super fan of anime and now you can rep his passion on the Jordan x Zion T-Shirt. Flex his favourite show on soft and heavyweight cotton that's perfect from workouts to hangouts.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Challenger Run Division
Description: When every run is a competition for more miles, our Challenger Shorts are there to take you through the finish. We tuned the Run Division version to provide smooth support that keeps you comfortable while you strive for a better time.

name: Nike Dri-FIT ADV AeroSwift
Description: Your hard work has got you to the starting line. Let the Nike Dri-FIT ADV AeroSwift Tights take you to the finish. Soft and smooth, with a lightweight, secure feel, these tights are geared to help you reach your personal best. This product is made with at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Paris Saint-Germain
Description: Flex your PSG fandom and rep Jordan heritage with shorts inspired by an iconic design. They're made from stretchy fabric that's easy to move in, with framed-in mesh panels that nod to MJ's pro kit.

name: Nike ACG Dri-FIT 'New Sands'
Description: Stay dry next time you hit the summit in these shorts. They're made from lightweight, sweat-wicking fabric that helps you stay dry. Time to tighten up the soft waistband and hit the trails.

name: Nike Dri-FIT UV
Category: Men's Standard Fit Golf Chino Trousers
Description: From the course to the concrete and everywhere in between, the Nike Dri-FIT UV Chino Trousers keep your look fresh. The stretchy design is slightly tapered from knee to hem, creating a tailored look that's built to perform.

name: Paris Saint-Germain
Category: Men's Nike Dri-FIT Pre-Match Football Top
Description: The Paris Saint-Germain Top gives you the same look as your favourite players. Sweat-wicking technology is lightweight and breathable to help keep you dry while you're warming up for the match. This product is made from 100% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Brazil 2022/23 Match Home
Category: Men's Nike Dri-FIT ADV Football Shirt
Description: Our "garra" is never done. Like other shirts from our Match collection, this one pairs authentic design details with lightweight, quick-drying fabric to help keep the world's biggest football stars cool and comfortable on the pitch.

name: Nike Dri-FIT LeBron
Description: Whether on the court or off, carry LeBron's motto of "Strive for Greatness" wherever you go. This soft, sweat-wicking tee has a relaxed feel so you can move comfortably while repping one of the best to ever play the game.

name: Giannis
Description: He's a freak of nature, a champion and power to behold on the court. Celebrate those qualities of Giannis by suiting up in these lightweight trousers. We made these with soft fleece so you stay comfortable beyond the court. Plus, they have an all-over, embossed graphic celebrating the MVP.

name: Jordan x Maison Château Rouge
Description: From Chicago to Paris and everywhere in between, these trousers let you rep the Jordan x MCR collab in crisp comfort. They feature an all-over print that tells a global story of youth connected through basketball culture. Front zips near the leg openings let you personalise the fit, rocking your bold look however feels best.

name: NikeCourt Dri-FIT Advantage
Description: Stretchy and breathable, the NikeCourt Dri-FIT Advantage Top will soon be your go-to for fast, fierce matches. Thanks to a new hybrid neckline, you'll get the look of a V-neck with the comfort of a crew. This product is made from at least 75% recycled polyester fibres.

name: Nike Everyday Lightweight
Description: Power through your workout with the Nike Everyday Lightweight Socks. Soft yarns with sweat-wicking technology help keep your feet comfortable and dry.

name: Nike Sportswear Sport Essentials
Description: The Nike Sportswear Sport Essentials Utility Shorts are all about adventure. A zip fly and snap closure provides a traditional cargo short feel. An elasticated waistband and internal drawcord ensure a comfortable, personalised fit. Snap-closed cargo pockets complete the look and provide additional storage to keep you ready for whatever comes next.

name: England
Description: Put your squad first in this England tee. Made from a soft knit fabric in a roomy fit, it lets you show off your national team pride in casual comfort.

name: Brazil
Description: Embrace a look that's bold in a top that blends football with skate style. A vibrant jaguar-inspired pattern nods to the national team's jerseys while a classic button-down design and stretchy sweat-wicking fabric help keep you cool when you're on the move.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Miler D.Y.E.
Description: Show off your brain on exercise in this sweat-wicking top. It's part of our Do You Even? Collection, which celebrates the positive effects of the run on your mind. Plus, it has all the things you expect from the Miler, like a smooth, breathable feel.

name: Los Angeles Lakers Statement Edition
Description: Emulate your favourite player in this Los Angeles Lakers jersey, a fan-ready favourite with logo and design details that match what the pros wear on the court. Plus, it infuses breathable mesh with sweat-wicking technology to help keep you cool and dry whether you're burning up the court or just keeping it casual around town.

name: Jordan Essential Holiday
Description: Who's ready for the festive season? You are, in this cosy hoodie. Made from brushed French terry in a classic festive checked pattern, it serves up nostalgic seasonal style and a hint of Jordan heritage.

name: Nike Forward Crew
Description: Nike Forward catapults your classic sweatshirt into the future. Unlike traditional knit fabrics, Nike Forward combines multiple thin layers of select fibres for an exceptionally lightweight feel that's effortlessly warm and comfortable. Plus, this first iteration of Nike Forward reduces the carbon footprint by an average of 75% (due to the use of recycled materials, lower process-energy use, and lower material density) when used instead of our traditional knit fleece materials. A lighter future is a brighter future. Join us for the journey Forward and let's experience it together.

name: Nike Air
Description: Ready for adventure? So are the Nike Sportswear Woven Shorts. Their breathable fabric help you lead the active life we all crave in the hotter months of the year. This product is made from at least 50% recycled nylon fibres.

name: Jordan 23 Engineered
Description: Stay ready for the weather and look effortlessly cool. This cosy sweatshirt is made from soft cotton for warmth and comfort. Minimal graphics let the stitching—inspired by MJ's iconic Wings jacket—shine through.

name: Nike Dri-FIT Starting 5
Description: Celebrate 40 years of Nike Force bringing energy to the court in our Starting 5 Jersey. Smooth, breathable fabric gives you a lightweight feel as you go coast-to-coast on the hardwood. It's an ode to an icon, with a relaxed fit that feels at home on the court and beyond.

name: LeBron James Lakers
Description: Pay tribute to your favourite player and their skills on the hardwood in this MVP jersey. Wear their name and number with pride while celebrating the NBA's 75th anniversary with diamond-themed details. Lightweight, breathable fabric wicks sweat to help you stay dry and cool while you're repping this pro.

name: Nike Dri-FIT
Description: Made from lightweight, sweat-wicking fabric, the Nike Dri-FIT T-Shirt feels comfy against your skin while you push your limits. Fresh, colourful graphics on the front and back give you a '90s throwback vibe.
